trans-unit.source: In addition to the two add methods, <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>, the SiteMapProviderCollection class supports the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> method to add an array of type <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>.
trans-unit.target: Além dos dois adicionar métodos <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>, a classe SiteMapProviderCollection suporta o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>método para adicionar uma matriz do tipo <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase%29>

trans-unit.source: The SiteMapProviderCollection is used by the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> class to track the set of <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> objects that are available to the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> during site map initialization.
trans-unit.target: O SiteMapProviderCollection é usado pelo <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>classe para controlar o conjunto de <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>objetos que estão disponíveis para o <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>durante a inicialização de mapa de site.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> </xref:System.Web.SiteMap>

trans-unit.source: However, the presence of a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> in the provider collection does not necessarily mean it is used by a <xref:System.Web.SiteMap> object, only that it is available for use.
trans-unit.target: No entanto, a presença de um <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>no provedor de coleção não significa necessariamente que é usado por um <xref:System.Web.SiteMap>do objeto, só que ele está disponível para uso.</xref:System.Web.SiteMap> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider> is stored in the SiteMapProviderCollection, the <xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A> property is used as the key.
trans-unit.target: Quando um <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>é armazenado em SiteMapProviderCollection, o <xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A>propriedade é usada como chave.</xref:System.Configuration.Provider.ProviderBase.Name%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> object that is returned by the <xref:System.Web.SiteMap.Providers%2A> property is read-only.

trans-unit.source: For this reason, you cannot use the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> methods to add additional providers programmatically at run time.
trans-unit.target: Por esse motivo, você não pode usar o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>métodos para adicionar provedores adicionais programaticamente no tempo de execução.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A> and <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> methods are used only in scenarios where you manually create site map provider objects and manage them with an instance of the <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Portanto, o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>e <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A>métodos são usados apenas em cenários onde você manualmente cria objetos de provedor de mapa do site e gerenciá-los com uma instância da <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection>classe.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.AddArray%2A> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.target: O método Add verifica o tipo do provedor especificado e, em seguida, chama o <xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>método para adicioná-lo à coleção.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapProviderCollection.Add%28System.Web.SiteMapProvider%29>
